# dotfiles-chezmoi

My dotfiles powered by [chezmoi](https://www.chezmoi.io).

## Setup

```bash
sh -c "$(wget -qO- get.chezmoi.io)" -- init --verbose --apply fgrehm/dotfiles-chezmoi
```

